virtualenv --python=python3.6 venv
venv/Scripts/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

I changed the pronounciation dictionary to suit my British accent. You can leave the default as is, or change words to suit your own accent
To use my dictionary:
Move the pronounciation-dict.dict file from Dict/ to venv/Lib/site-packages/speech_recognition/pocketsphinx-data/en-US/